    • Uses of GenericController in control

      Subclasses of GenericController in control 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AddTagController
      AddTagController is the controller for adding a tag to the selected photo in the album page
      class  CaptionController
      CaptionController is the controller for the caption page, allowing the user to input a caption into their photo
      class  CopyController
      CopyController is controls copying a photo from one album into another, while keeping it in the album it is currently in
      class  DeleteTagController
      DeleteTagController is a tag which controls the deletion of a tag from a photo
      class  DisplayController
      DisplayController manages the display of a selected photo in a view which allows them to see the date the photo was last modified, a list of tags, the caption, and the image
      class  MoveController
      MoveController is a class which controls the movement of a photo from one album into another while deleting it from the first
